title: READY FOR YOU! .. Cook's Kitchen Island plus New Appliances, Cabinets
posting_body: ['Enjoy The Good Life...', 'Welcome Home!', 'Seize your chance to live in The Irvington, one of the most iconic apartment communities in Portland, OR.', 'The Irvington', 'show contact info', '1532 NE 21st Avenue', 'Portland OR 97232', 'Bed: 1', 'Bath: 1', 'Rent: 1449', 'We offer our residents a myriad of top-notch amenities to make life that much easier so that you have more time to kick back.', 'The Irvington provides residents with roomy one-bedroom apartment floor plans with modern design and filled with closets, so you can find the home that fits your lifestyle for years to come.', 'Got some downtime and need to unwind?', 'If you want somewhere serene to clear your head, you need look no further than our smoke-free community with long private balconies, gated off-street parking, free bike storage, and parcel lockers.', 'Our Walk Score of 87 makes us as a “Very Walkable” location and our Bike Score of 100 makes us a “Biker’s Paradise”.', 'Rest assured, you can explore the area and nearby Portland with or without a car.', 'Our community offers you the very best of the city from the peaceful confines of the historic Irvington and Sullivan’s Gulch neighborhoods.', 'At The Irvington, we get that life can sometimes get hectic, busy, or just downright stressful.', 'Our Amenities', 'Cat-friendly', 'White Quartz Countertops', 'Alarm System', 'Elevator Access to Floors 2-6', 'Private Deck / Patio with Living Room and Bedroom Access', 'New Carpet in the Bedroom', 'Kitchen Island that doubles as a Breakfast Bar', 'Gated Covered or Uncovered Parking*', 'Abundant Closet Space Throughout', 'Private Exterior Storage Closet', 'Historic Irvington Neighborhood', 'Light Oak Hardwood Floors in All Living Areas', 'Interior Parcel Lockers and mail boxes', 'Maple Soft-Close Cabinets', 'Convenient Laundry Facility in Building', 'Controlled Access Building Entry', 'Walk Score 89, Bike Score 100', 'Full Tub/Shower, Lighted Mirror w/ LED lighting', 'Professionally Managed by Princeton Property Management', 'Your home is your castle and a place to unwind and relax.', 'Live next-door to the heart of Portland’s hustle and bustle!', 'With easy access to I-84 and I-5, The Irvington is just minutes away from Downtown Portland and The Pearl District.', 'The Irvington offers something for everyone.', 'See our available amenities to find something that speaks to you.', 'Get a sneak peek of the good life here at The Irvington.', 'If you just need to get away and enjoy the city’s offerings, explore all of the shopping, dining, and entertainment that nearby downtown Portland has to offer!']
